Dialogue: 10,0:00:43.07,0:00:48.80,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Do you remember the palace of Frosgar, {probably alludes to https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Fredensborg_Palace }
Dialogue: 10,0:00:49.93,0:00:53.81,Narrator,,0,0,0,,{sunk deep in fear of the fiends?}that was steeped in fear of the fiends?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:55.99,0:01:00.95,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Do you remember the witch Grendel,
Dialogue: 10,0:01:02.30,0:01:06.18,Narrator,,0,0,0,,who stole people, tore them apart, and ate them?
Dialogue: 10,0:01:08.76,0:01:14.06,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Do you remember that battle in the deep waters,
Dialogue: 10,0:01:15.44,0:01:18.73,Narrator,,0,0,0,,{where evil dragons and serpents lurked?}where evil dragons and venomous serpents lurked?
Dialogue: 10,0:01:21.24,0:01:23.71,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Do you remember...
Dialogue: 10,0:01:24.27,0:01:27.80,Narrator,,0,0,0,,the blue-black sea of Zealand,
Dialogue: 10,0:01:28.53,0:01:31.95,Narrator,,0,0,0,,dyed red with the witch's blood?
Dialogue: 10,0:01:33.48,0:01:36.05,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Do you remember...
Dialogue: 10,0:01:36.90,0:01:39.75,Narrator,,0,0,0,,the great victory feast,
Dialogue: 10,0:01:41.08,0:01:45.21,Narrator,,0,0,0,,{held in the royal palace, honoring unmatched valor?}{??? idk what's that kibuku}held in the royal palace to celebrate\N truly unmatched valor?{武勲 }
Dialogue: 10,0:01:52.47,0:01:55.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Wrecked it! Wrecked it!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:55.26,0:01:57.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{What's this, an egg?}{referring to how easily it broke}It crumpled like an eggshell!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:58.89,0:02:01.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Our ancestors are gonna be mad at you, Jack.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:01.34,0:02:03.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Quit complaining and get on.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:03.46,0:02:04.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Tch.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:04.50,0:02:06.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Again?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:06.43,0:02:08.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Hey, where'd Pooh go? {puuko = プー公 - literally "prince poo" - shortening of 子グマのプー公 = Winnie the Pooh}
Dialogue: 10,0:02:08.62,0:02:09.36,Default,,0,0,0,,No idea.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:16.54,0:02:17.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Pooh!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:18.96,0:02:20.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Pooh!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:20.59,0:02:21.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Pooh!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:21.96,0:02:23.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Pooh!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:31.93,0:02:33.84,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing? We're leaving!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:34.26,0:02:36.72,Default,,0,0,0,,My stomach hurts.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:36.72,0:02:39.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Playing sick won't work. Come down already.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:39.72,0:02:43.73,Default,,0,0,0,,No way! You're just gonna dump me in the swamp again!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:43.73,0:02:47.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Not coming? Fine, if you won't come down, I'll come up!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:09.24,0:03:12.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Yahoo! Yahoo!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:12.63,0:03:14.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Full steam ahead!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:14.49,0:03:16.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{Here we go!}{itadaki?}Pedal to the metal!{"buttobase"}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.47,0:03:20.38,Song,,0,0,0,,Ah! Heigh-ho!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.38,0:03:24.50,Song,,0,0,0,,{ジャックの唄 / Jack's song - all songs here were written for this movie so unless there are magically CD (if they even received one) scans there, safe to assume nothing here will have lyrics, so going by ear}So off we go, even if there's no road to drive on!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.71,0:03:27.73,Song,,0,0,0,,Heigh-ho! Heigh-ho!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.73,0:03:32.90,Song,,0,0,0,,So everywhere's my highway!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.90,0:03:39.40,Song,,0,0,0,,{I'll never get lost, if anywhere is my road}{???}I'll never get lost! \NIf I do, I'll find my way again!{"maigo ni naranai, nareba mitsukeru dake sa"}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.74,0:03:42.72,Song,,0,0,0,,Heigh-ho! Heigh-ho!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.72,0:03:48.34,Song,,0,0,0,,{So let's find our friends and our dreams!}Let's depart in search of new friends and new dreams!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:17.65,0:04:18.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:22.03,0:04:23.55,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:23.55,0:04:24.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone's riding it.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:29.00,0:04:31.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? It's some weird girl!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:42.32,0:04:44.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Tch. She's getting on my nerves.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:44.83,0:04:46.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's catch her! Catch her!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:46.95,0:04:47.98,Default,,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:40.99,0:05:43.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Well? Pretty impressive, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:43.16,0:05:44.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:45.44,0:05:47.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Pipe down. {/shut up}
Dialogue: 10,0:05:47.87,0:05:50.76,Default,,0,0,0,,What's so great about that weird contraption? \N{We won't lose to it.}You'll never beat us!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:51.25,0:05:52.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{Such a show-off.}{?? idk, maybe "Stubborn"}You're such a show-off.{"oo-tsuppari"}
Dialogue: 10,0:05:57.88,0:05:59.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{So it's this?}So this is how it looks up close?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:01.26,0:06:03.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{Hey, isn't that the final boss of bamboo copters?}{yes, I don't know how, but they used video game slang in 1967; https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Bamboo-copter }Hey, isn't that the big boss of all bamboo copters? {in 1967, this likely refers to workspace bosses or crime bosses; "final boss" is too modern of a wording}
Dialogue: 10,0:06:03.86,0:06:07.37,Default,,0,0,0,,You should be embarrassed, \Nnot knowing this thing... I mean, uh...
Dialogue: 10,0:06:07.37,0:06:08.82,Default,,0,0,0,,It's called a helicopter.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:09.50,0:06:11.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Right. Exactly.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:11.29,0:06:12.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey, let me ride it!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:13.19,0:06:15.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes! Me too!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:15.03,0:06:16.50,Default,,0,0,0,,And me!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:16.50,0:06:19.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't it way nicer than Jack's car?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:21.16,0:06:22.69,Default,,0,0,0,,What about you, Jack?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:23.15,0:06:24.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you wanna fly it?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:24.82,0:06:26.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not interested in all that!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:27.87,0:06:30.33,Default,,0,0,0,,But... I guess I could, just for a bit.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:30.77,0:06:32.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{You're so phony.}Don't be so difficult.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:33.02,0:06:35.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Just admit you {\i1}do{\i0} want to ride it.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:35.13,0:06:37.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{Fine, if it's Jack, I'll let him on.}{meaning she won't let anyone else}Fine. I don't mind making an exception for you.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:37.77,0:06:40.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, that's not fair!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:40.17,0:06:43.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{You can't do that to us, why only Jack?}You can't do that to us. \NWhy does he get better treatment?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:43.50,0:06:45.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It's unfair! Unfair!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:45.50,0:06:46.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{Disgraceful! Disgraceful!}Foul play! Foul play!{liberal; she says "fuheikou" as a pun on the cat's "fukouhei"}
Dialogue: 10,0:06:46.92,0:06:46.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\clip(341,301,592,353)}{Disgraceful! Disgraceful!}Foul play! Foul play!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:46.96,0:06:47.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{Disgraceful! Disgraceful!\alpha&HFF&}Foul {\alpha&H0&}play! Foul play!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:47.01,0:06:47.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\clip(392,290.4,598.4,357.6)}{Disgraceful! Disgraceful!}Foul play! Foul play!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:47.05,0:06:47.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\clip(416,285.6,615.2,353.6)}{Disgraceful! Disgraceful!}Foul play! Foul play!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:47.09,0:06:47.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\clip(442.4,282.4,620.8,352)}{Disgraceful! Disgraceful!}Foul play! Foul play!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:47.13,0:06:47.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\clip(465.6,304,647.2,353.6)}{Disgraceful! Disgraceful!}Foul play! Foul play!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:47.17,0:06:47.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\clip(491,301.6,616.8,348.8)}{Disgraceful! Disgraceful!}Foul play! Foul play!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:47.21,0:06:47.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\clip(516,291.2,688,349.6)}{Disgraceful! Disgraceful!}Foul play! Foul play!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:52.50,0:06:54.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Bye!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:54.50,0:06:56.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Tch. He's mocking us!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:56.33,0:06:57.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{This is boring.}How lame.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:01.19,0:07:02.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{Amazing!}What a view!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:05.04,0:07:06.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Squeaky!{チュウ公 - reference to https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/The_Tale_of_Mrs._Tittlemouse - translated into japanese as "chuuchuu-san" - unlike winnie, I don't think "Tit" or "tittle" would fit here as the name}{Note: full name of "Tittlemouse" can work too, no need to shorten it. Could also adapt the name as Squeaky. Leaving the final say to the editor.}
Dialogue: 10,0:07:07.11,0:07:09.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry to intrude!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:09.08,0:07:10.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Pretty sneaky.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:10.79,0:07:13.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{You may try to be clever and ride it alone,}You tried to pull a fast one on us,
Dialogue: 10,0:07:13.91,0:07:16.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{but it won't work on me, Jack.}but I won't fall for that, Jack.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:29.50,0:07:31.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{How far did Jack go anyway?}How far will she take Jack?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:31.65,0:07:36.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry. It's Jack, so we know he'll come back.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:36.33,0:07:39.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, but he's such a scatterbrain!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:43.57,0:07:45.57,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the scatterbrain here!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:55.24,0:08:58.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, hold on! I've got a bad feeling about this.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:14.62,0:09:16.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{Hey, over there too!}Look! There's another one!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:58.06,0:10:00.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa... a giant mirror.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:00.06,0:10:01.34,Default,,0,0,0,,But something's wrong.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:02.06,0:10:03.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, right.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:03.14,0:10:05.14,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the demon castle. {idk how he knows that; akuma = devil}
Dialogue: 10,0:10:16.50,0:10:18.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Another one.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:19.27,0:10:22.98,Default,,0,0,0,,That makes thirteen today.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:23.44,0:10:27.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Unlucky, yet delightful.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:32.95,0:10:36.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll fill the whole world with my children.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:37.87,0:10:41.20,Default,,0,0,0,,What a wonderful world it will be.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:41.20,0:10:43.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I can hardly wait.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:08.28,0:11:09.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! Squeaky!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:10.75,0:11:12.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Squeaky! Squeaky!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:13.63,0:11:14.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Squeaky!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:14.32,0:11:17.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{No no no no! Quit dawdling \Nand let him go inside already!}Come on! Stop wasting time! Pull him in already!{he's addressing the demon on the other side, not Jack. And it's やいやい, not いいやいいや}
Dialogue: 10,0:11:19.20,0:11:21.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Squeaky! Squeaky! Squeaky!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:28.83,0:11:30.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, what's gonna happen to Squeaky?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:30.92,0:11:35.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyone who goes in there \Nturns into a fine demon, that's what!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:36.60,0:11:37.93,Default,,0,0,0,,A demon?!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:39.18,0:11:40.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{probably yells of pain/shock}Ow!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:41.52,0:11:44.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Thief! Dirtbag! Pumpkin-head!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:54.56,0:11:58.50,Song,,0,0,0,,This one too! This one too!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:58.50,0:12:00.50,Song,,0,0,0,,Horses, cows, humans—
Dialogue: 10,0:12:00.50,0:12:02.53,Song,,0,0,0,,Just watch!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:02.53,0:12:08.54,Song,,0,0,0,,{Our fun is just beginning!}See how frightening we are!{"oretachi no osoroshisa"}
Dialogue: 10,0:12:08.54,0:12:11.84,Song,,0,0,0,,{More more more more!}Inside you go! Inside you go! {"naka-naka"}
Dialogue: 10,0:12:12.44,0:12:16.42,Song,,0,0,0,,{pika pika pika aya}Shine! Sparkle! Glimmer! \NShine! Sparkle! Glimmer! (What...?)
Dialogue: 10,0:12:16.42,0:12:17.92,Song,,0,0,0,,Squeeze! Squeeze! Squeeze!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:17.92,0:12:18.50,Song,,0,0,0,,Ouch!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:18.50,0:12:19.92,Song,,0,0,0,,Clang! Clang! Clang!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:19.92,0:12:21.38,Song,,0,0,0,,Boom! Zap!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:21.38,0:12:22.33,Song,,0,0,0,,{probably hammer / sound of slamming?}Slam!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:22.33,0:12:23.39,Song,,0,0,0,,It tickles!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:23.39,0:12:24.89,Song,,0,0,0,,Slam! Clang! Bang!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:30.35,0:12:34.28,Song,,0,0,0,,{Turn into demons and hurry up!}Hurry up and turn into demons!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:38.24,0:12:40.18,Song,,0,0,0,,{Shall we roast them and eat with sauce?}Should we roast them and eat them with sauce?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:40.18,0:12:44.12,Song,,0,0,0,,{Or boil them and eat with soy? What do you think?}Or boil them and eat them with soy, perhaps?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:02.14,0:13:03.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{Get him!}{?????  maybe "totta" = "he took [one of ours]"}He snatched one!{totta zo}
Dialogue: 10,0:13:06.14,0:13:09.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop! What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:09.83,0:13:13.14,Default,,0,0,0,,It's me, Jack! We gotta get out of here!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:13.78,0:13:17.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Leggo! Leave me alone, you pest.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:17.88,0:13:20.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{Hey, get a grip! Don't you...}Hey, snap out of it! Don't you...
Dialogue: 10,0:13:20.07,0:13:22.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Grab him!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:22.16,0:13:27.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, stop! Stop! Yeah, stop!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:27.68,0:13:31.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold it right there! \NWe've got him cornered!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:34.33,0:13:37.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe he jumped so high!{"anna tokoro, yoku mo...!"}
Dialogue: 10,0:13:37.18,0:13:38.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Is he for real?!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:38.88,0:13:39.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Pull him down!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:00.48,0:14:01.47,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:15.38,0:14:17.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Help me!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:17.38,0:14:20.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Let go of the rope! Let go!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:20.37,0:14:22.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, right...
Dialogue: 10,0:14:25.01,0:14:27.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{There, catch it!}Catch! Now, pull!{"sore, hikkakero"}
Dialogue: 10,0:14:30.31,0:14:32.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't breathe!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:32.81,0:14:36.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Jack escaped outside! After him! After him!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:49.41,0:14:50.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Ow!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:55.38,0:14:56.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{What's this?}So that's where he is?{"koko da na"}
Dialogue: 10,0:15:06.10,0:15:08.02,Default,,0,0,0,,He tricked me!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:09.58,0:15:11.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Bye-bye!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:11.94,0:15:13.77,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll pay for this!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:57.85,0:16:00.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Shibari, how'd you let something like this happen?! {her little brother; shibari means "to tie/bind [something with a rope]" and his special trick is a rope }
Dialogue: 10,0:16:00.19,0:16:03.34,Default,,0,0,0,,So what? We'll catch him again.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:04.20,0:16:06.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{Not one slip-up is allowed!}Not a single slip-up is allowed!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:06.42,0:16:11.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{If Lady Grendel finds out, \Ndo you know what she'll do to us?!}If Lady Grendel finds out, \Ndo you realize what she'll do to us?!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:39.15,0:16:40.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Jack!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:41.03,0:16:43.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's you guys?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:43.11,0:16:46.36,Default,,0,0,0,,We got worried, so we came looking.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:46.36,0:16:48.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Where were you?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:48.11,0:16:50.47,Default,,0,0,0,,That girl was a demon! {akuma}
Dialogue: 10,0:16:50.47,0:16:52.52,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a demon castle past here!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:56.12,0:16:58.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Demons! Demons are coming!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:58.87,0:16:59.97,Default,,0,0,0,,It's true!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:59.97,0:17:02.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Run! If you get caught, you're done for!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:05.97,0:17:07.93,Default,,0,0,0,,This is bad!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:24.67,0:18:26.17,Default,,0,0,0,,All right...
Dialogue: 10,0:18:28.84,0:18:30.01,Default,,0,0,0,,There!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:33.14,0:18:35.43,Default,,0,0,0,,How do you like {\i1}that{\i0}?!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:42.04,0:18:45.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{???? maybe "don't give up"}And pull! And pull!\NYou won't catch us so easily!{"wasshoi" + "nameru na"}
Dialogue: 10,0:18:59.64,0:19:01.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{We nailed you, you clumsy demon!}Now you've gone and done it, clumsy demon!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:01.68,0:19:04.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{Look at this foolish, good-for-nothing lump talking!}{???? some elaborate insult}What was that, good-for-nothing coward?!{"ikujinashi no konkonchiki-me"}
Dialogue: 10,0:19:04.65,0:19:06.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{Look at this failure of a demon talking!}Right back at you, failure of a demon!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:07.23,0:19:09.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{I feel ashamed!}You'll pay for this!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:09.34,0:19:10.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{How do you like that?!}You had it coming!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:10.71,0:19:12.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, time to see the witch!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:12.84,0:19:13.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Heave-ho!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:13.84,0:19:15.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Heave-ho...
Dialogue: 10,0:19:17.78,0:19:19.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Serves you right! {lit: good feeling}
Dialogue: 10,0:19:55.99,0:20:02.16,Song,,0,0,0,,Come on, let's get along!\N There's no need to hold back anymore!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:02.17,0:20:08.06,Song,,0,0,0,,{Tthere's no need for logic, let's dance happily!}No more excuses! Let's dance happily!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:18.99,0:20:26.96,Song,,0,0,0,,{Raise your knees in dance, stomp your shyness, \Nstomp your feet,}Dance on! Raise your knees! \NStomp your feet to the beat!{"odoro yo, hiza te ni agete, -- wo kurikaeshi, ashi fundoke"}
Dialogue: 10,0:20:28.29,0:20:31.08,Song,,0,0,0,,{and let's dance love!}{honestly can't hear shit}Don't hold back! Let's dance!{"saa te, odorou yo"}
Dialogue: 10,0:20:26.96,0:20:27.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Ouch!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:59.37,0:21:01.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, everyone!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:01.43,0:21:02.28,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!{"nanda"}
Dialogue: 10,0:21:03.37,0:21:04.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Heads up!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:04.81,0:21:05.97,Default,,0,0,0,,A demon is here.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:07.29,0:21:09.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Find it and take it down!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:18.84,0:21:21.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Do it! Do it!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:25.10,0:21:27.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice! Keep it up!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:27.45,0:21:28.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Shibari!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:36.50,0:21:37.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Take that!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:37.61,0:21:39.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Have a taste of this!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:40.90,0:21:43.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Catch! Here's another one!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:43.67,0:21:44.81,Default,,0,0,0,,There!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:44.16,0:21:45.37,Overlap,,0,0,0,,Here's one more!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:48.26,0:21:49.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Go! Take her down!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:49.79,0:21:50.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Why, you...
Dialogue: 10,0:21:50.50,0:21:52.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice! {Let's go!}We did it!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:52.90,0:21:55.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah! Hold her down!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:55.10,0:21:57.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop struggling, will you?!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:57.48,0:21:58.71,Default,,0,0,0,,You little...
Dialogue: 10,0:21:58.71,0:22:01.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice going! Nice going!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:01.55,0:22:04.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{How's that, huh?!}{?}That'll teach you! Give up?!{"sore, donna koitsu, maita ka?"}
Dialogue: 10,0:22:08.14,0:22:09.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Spare me...
Dialogue: 10,0:22:15.06,0:22:16.61,Default,,0,0,0,,She's gone!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:16.61,0:22:17.63,Default,,0,0,0,,How frustrating!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:17.63,0:22:20.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{I hate this!}{\fad(0,1000)}I can't stand her!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:56.63,0:22:59.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Kiki, don't you feel ashamed?
Dialogue: 10,0:22:59.77,0:23:02.02,Default,,0,0,0,,You let the kid you kidnapped get away!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:02.02,0:23:03.65,Default,,0,0,0,,You owe everyone an apology!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:03.65,0:23:05.74,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right! Apologize!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:05.74,0:23:08.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Apologize!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:08.46,0:23:10.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Returning defeated is a disgrace for a demon!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:10.70,0:23:13.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's right, that's right! Apologize!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:13.77,0:23:15.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Say you're sorry!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:41.65,0:23:45.36,Default,,0,0,0,,How about we go tell Lady Grendel on you?
Dialogue: 10,0:23:45.83,0:23:48.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure, go right ahead!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:48.00,0:23:51.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{But don't you have a shred of decency or pity for Kiki?}But don't you feel sorry for Kiki? \NShe did all she could!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:51.62,0:23:54.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Idiot! A demon isn't allowed a single failure!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:54.79,0:23:56.75,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:56.75,0:23:59.17,Default,,0,0,0,,The Witch is terrifying!
Dialogue: 10,0:24:00.21,0:24:02.61,Default,,0,0,0,,You're doomed!
Dialogue: 10,0:24:03.26,0:24:05.19,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll regret it!
Dialogue: 10,0:24:05.19,0:24:07.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Failure means death.
Dialogue: 10,0:24:07.15,0:24:09.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Death!
Dialogue: 10,0:24:13.06,0:24:15.89,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll get frozen solid.
Dialogue: 10,0:24:15.89,0:24:18.31,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll get frozen solid...
Dialogue: 10,0:24:22.36,0:24:25.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, just die!
Dialogue: 10,0:24:48.90,0:24:51.87,Thought,,0,0,0,,{I saw it, I really saw it!}She saw me. She really saw me!
Dialogue: 10,0:24:51.87,0:24:53.81,Thought,,0,0,0,,The Witch knows everything.
Dialogue: 10,0:24:55.35,0:25:00.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, Kiki. \N{Tomorrow is another day.}Let tomorrow take care of itself.
Dialogue: 10,0:25:11.60,0:25:16.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Kiki, I saw everything with my own eyes.
Dialogue: 10,0:25:16.12,0:25:21.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard of your failure with my own ears.
Dialogue: 10,0:25:21.73,0:25:23.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{Prepare yourself}You embarrassed yourself.
Dialogue: 10,0:25:24.51,0:25:26.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{for the shame.}Get ready for the worst.
Dialogue: 10,0:26:39.04,0:26:41.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Help!
Dialogue: 10,0:26:43.86,0:26:45.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Our house is flying!
Dialogue: 10,0:26:49.78,0:26:53.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What's going on here?!
Dialogue: 10,0:26:55.18,0:26:56.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't let go!
Dialogue: 10,0:26:57.22,0:26:58.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 10,0:27:02.77,0:27:04.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{??? maybe yoshi}Up we go.
Dialogue: 10,0:27:04.05,0:27:06.33,Default,,0,0,0,,A d-demon...
Dialogue: 10,0:27:08.53,0:27:09.86,Default,,0,0,0,,All right...
Dialogue: 10,0:27:10.27,0:27:12.28,Default,,0,0,0,,This is bad!
Dialogue: 10,0:27:12.28,0:27:13.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Demon! Demon!
Dialogue: 10,0:27:15.83,0:27:17.85,Default,,0,0,0,,What's happening?!
Dialogue: 10,0:27:17.85,0:27:19.53,Default,,0,0,0,,It's her again!
Dialogue: 10,0:27:22.04,0:27:24.54,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, watch this!
Dialogue: 10,0:27:30.59,0:27:32.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, demon! Don't play dirty!
Dialogue: 10,0:27:32.64,0:27:34.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You let your guard down!
Dialogue: 10,0:27:35.07,0:27:36.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Give us back our house!
Dialogue: 10,0:27:36.68,0:27:37.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Or what?
Dialogue: 10,0:27:37.95,0:27:39.18,Default,,0,0,0,,You little...
Dialogue: 10,0:28:21.39,0:28:24.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? This is bad! What's going on?
Dialogue: 10,0:28:37.51,0:28:38.33,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 10,0:28:58.93,0:29:01.74,Default,,0,0,0,,She's dead! Attaboy! {"good feeling" again}
Dialogue: 10,0:29:01.74,0:29:04.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Serves her right!
Dialogue: 10,0:29:05.14,0:29:07.10,Default,,0,0,0,,We got her!
Dialogue: 10,0:29:07.62,0:29:09.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's just finish her off, Jack!
Dialogue: 10,0:29:08.62,0:29:09.29,Overlap,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 10,0:29:09.67,0:29:10.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 10,0:29:10.85,0:29:12.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{Let's take her home.}{look after / nurse}Let's help her.
Dialogue: 10,0:29:12.54,0:29:13.65,Default,,0,0,0,,How come?!
Dialogue: 10,0:29:13.65,0:29:15.53,Default,,0,0,0,,She's a demon!
Dialogue: 10,0:29:15.53,0:29:19.66,Default,,0,0,0,,But don't you pity her? \NShe's practically dying.
Dialogue: 10,0:29:30.96,0:29:32.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are we doing this?
Dialogue: 10,0:29:32.11,0:29:35.90,Default,,0,0,0,,She bullied us all this time \Nand even wrecked our house.
Dialogue: 10,0:29:35.90,0:29:38.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Helping her makes no sense.
Dialogue: 10,0:29:38.05,0:29:40.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Jack must've lost his mind.
Dialogue: 10,0:29:40.90,0:29:41.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:29:41.74,0:29:43.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I know, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:29:43.10,0:29:44.24,Default,,0,0,0,,He's weird.
Dialogue: 10,0:29:44.24,0:29:45.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Really, really weird.
Dialogue: 10,0:29:45.53,0:29:46.31,Default,,0,0,0,,A total weirdo.
Dialogue: 10,0:29:46.31,0:29:49.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{She could die for all we care!}{???}I don't care what happens to her!
Dialogue: 10,0:29:49.58,0:29:50.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 10,0:30:10.18,0:30:13.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't we tell you?
Dialogue: 10,0:30:12.58,0:30:13.04,Overlap,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:30:13.04,0:30:16.22,Default,,0,0,0,,There should be a limit to kindness. {good-naturedness}
Dialogue: 10,0:30:15.55,0:30:16.22,Overlap,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 10,0:30:18.23,0:30:19.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 10,0:31:28.46,0:31:30.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{He's here...}Ouch, that hurt...
Dialogue: 10,0:31:31.92,0:31:35.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, demons!
Dialogue: 10,0:31:35.71,0:31:38.34,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'm not a demon... {maybe a pun on bear = kuma / demon = akuma}
Dialogue: 10,0:31:43.38,0:31:45.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Charge! Get him!
Dialogue: 10,0:31:53.78,0:31:54.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Ready!
Dialogue: 10,0:31:55.30,0:31:56.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 10,0:32:01.29,0:32:02.40,Default,,0,0,0,,He's beaten me!
Dialogue: 10,0:32:04.20,0:32:05.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{C'mere!}{sore?}Take that!
Dialogue: 10,0:32:32.64,0:32:34.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Everybody out!
Dialogue: 10,0:32:34.71,0:32:36.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{Hey, let's run while we can.}{kakureru can mean a dozen things and idk what it is here}Hey, let's take cover while we can.
Dialogue: 10,0:32:41.33,0:32:42.78,Default,,0,0,0,,It's your turn.
Dialogue: 10,0:32:42.78,0:32:44.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, after you.
Dialogue: 10,0:32:44.35,0:32:46.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Go on, go on, don't be shy.
Dialogue: 10,0:32:46.78,0:32:48.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Then let's fly together, yeah?
Dialogue: 10,0:32:48.78,0:32:50.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's fly like good friends.
Dialogue: 10,0:32:51.40,0:32:52.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Here we go.
Dialogue: 10,0:33:45.58,0:33:46.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 10,0:33:46.62,0:33:48.75,Default,,0,0,0,,What a huge windmill!
Dialogue: 10,0:33:48.75,0:33:53.18,Default,,0,0,0,,What do they use something like that for?
Dialogue: 10,0:33:53.18,0:33:55.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{No idea.}{???}Are you really that dumb?{"gaku ga nai ne"}
Dialogue: 10,0:33:55.08,0:33:57.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{Probably generating electricity.}Generating electricity, most likely.
Dialogue: 10,0:33:57.48,0:33:58.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:33:58.14,0:34:02.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? But why would they need that electricity?
Dialogue: 10,0:34:23.70,0:34:25.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew you'd come.
Dialogue: 10,0:34:26.29,0:34:28.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You came to look for Squeaky, didn't you?
Dialogue: 10,0:34:28.50,0:34:30.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go. Get her!
Dialogue: 10,0:34:30.22,0:34:31.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 10,0:34:31.51,0:34:33.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait a minute!
Dialogue: 10,0:34:33.50,0:34:35.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I've changed my mind.
Dialogue: 10,0:34:35.15,0:34:37.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll help you.
Dialogue: 10,0:34:37.10,0:34:38.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Lies!
Dialogue: 10,0:34:38.76,0:34:40.47,Default,,0,0,0,,We're not falling for that.
Dialogue: 10,0:34:40.47,0:34:42.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't sweet-talk us!
Dialogue: 10,0:34:42.51,0:34:44.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't get it.
Dialogue: 10,0:34:46.89,0:34:50.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I guess you don't want me\N to guide you to Squeaky?
Dialogue: 10,0:34:51.41,0:34:53.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Jack! Don't let her fool you!
Dialogue: 10,0:34:53.60,0:34:54.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:35:00.60,0:35:02.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, someone's coming from over there too!
Dialogue: 10,0:35:04.60,0:35:07.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry, hide here, everyone, quick!
Dialogue: 10,0:35:12.64,0:35:14.76,Default,,0,0,0,,This way, hurry!
Dialogue: 10,0:35:53.09,0:35:54.99,Default,,0,0,0,,He's just like me!
Dialogue: 10,0:36:11.99,0:36:13.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait for me!
Dialogue: 10,0:36:14.88,0:36:16.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, wait up!
Dialogue: 10,0:36:25.27,0:36:26.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 10,0:36:29.87,0:36:31.21,Default,,0,0,0,,That's him! {yarou}
Dialogue: 10,0:36:37.30,0:36:38.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on!
Dialogue: 10,0:36:38.51,0:36:40.35,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, get him!
Dialogue: 10,0:36:38.51,0:36:40.35,Overlap,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 10,0:36:42.18,0:36:52.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Heave-ho! Heave-ho! Heave-ho!\NHeave-ho! Heave-ho! Heave-ho! Heave-ho!
Dialogue: 10,0:36:53.40,0:36:56.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Calling yourself a demon without knowing basic manners. {i guess again because he's a bear = kuma, somehow?}
Dialogue: 10,0:36:56.09,0:36:59.43,Default,,0,0,0,,If you walk around naked, Lady Grendel will scold you!
Dialogue: 10,0:37:02.25,0:37:05.71,Default,,0,0,0,,They want me to wear that too?
Dialogue: 10,0:37:06.81,0:37:08.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! Found it!
Dialogue: 10,0:37:10.25,0:37:12.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh my, it looks so good on me!
Dialogue: 10,0:39:25.35,0:39:27.18,Default,,0,0,0,,No, definitely fry him.
Dialogue: 10,0:39:27.18,0:39:28.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's grill him!
Dialogue: 10,0:39:28.41,0:39:29.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's simmer him.
Dialogue: 10,0:39:29.74,0:39:30.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's boil him. {nitsuke = vegetables or fish boiled in soy sauce}
Dialogue: 10,0:39:30.74,0:39:31.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe steam him? {mushiyaki = baking foods in a covered pan; foods baked in a covered pan}
Dialogue: 10,0:39:31.83,0:39:32.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I say skewer him. {kishiyaki =  grilling on a skewer; spit-roasting}
Dialogue: 10,0:39:32.87,0:39:33.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I say fry him in butter.
Dialogue: 10,0:39:33.90,0:39:35.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I say fry him in oil.
Dialogue: 10,0:39:35.16,0:39:36.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I say make a steak.
Dialogue: 10,0:39:36.20,0:39:37.33,Default,,0,0,0,,How about tempura? {tempura; deep-fried fish and vegetables in a light batter​}
Dialogue: 10,0:39:37.33,0:39:38.19,Default,,0,0,0,,No, definitely fried!
Dialogue: 10,0:39:38.19,0:39:39.75,Default,,0,0,0,,How about a barbecue?
Dialogue: 10,0:39:39.75,0:39:41.92,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right, let's have some barbecue.
Dialogue: 10,0:39:41.92,0:39:44.67,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right. Barbecue sounds great.
Dialogue: 10,0:39:44.67,0:39:47.84,Default,,0,0,0,,But Jack looks tough, \Nso he'll be hard to cook.
Dialogue: 10,0:39:47.84,0:39:49.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Jack is tender.
Dialogue: 10,0:39:49.24,0:39:50.22,Default,,0,0,0,,He'll cook fast.
Dialogue: 10,0:39:50.85,0:39:53.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Jack barbecue!
Dialogue: 10,0:39:53.02,0:39:55.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, Jack?
Dialogue: 10,0:39:57.31,0:39:58.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Barbecue!
Dialogue: 10,0:39:58.40,0:40:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's simmer him.
Dialogue: 10,0:39:58.40,0:40:00.00,Overlap,,0,0,0,,Barbecue!
Dialogue: 10,0:40:00.00,0:40:02.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's steam him!
Dialogue: 10,0:40:00.00,0:40:02.34,Overlap,,0,0,0,,No, skewer him!
Dialogue: 10,0:40:02.34,0:40:03.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{Let's skewer him!}I say fry him in butter.
Dialogue: 10,0:40:03.65,0:40:04.95,Default,,0,0,0,,No, fry him in oil!
Dialogue: 10,0:40:04.95,0:40:05.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I want steak!
Dialogue: 10,0:40:05.86,0:40:06.91,Default,,0,0,0,,How about tempura?
Dialogue: 10,0:40:06.91,0:40:08.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I want him deep-fried!
Dialogue: 10,0:40:08.39,0:40:09.68,Default,,0,0,0,,So how do we cook him?
