Dialogue: 10,0:43:50.94,0:43:51.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Barbecue...
Dialogue: 10,0:43:51.99,0:43:52.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Barbecue!
Dialogue: 10,0:43:52.94,0:43:53.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Barbecue.
Dialogue: 10,0:44:12.01,0:44:16.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{Listen closely!}See? Told you so!{"sou da, goran"} \NWhenever I want something, I never let go of it.
Dialogue: 10,0:44:16.28,0:44:18.97,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter what, \Nyou'll turn into a demon in the end.
Dialogue: 10,0:44:44.54,0:44:48.49,Song,,0,0,0,,That one too! And that one! {koitsu mo? same song as before}
Dialogue: 10,0:44:48.49,0:44:51.91,Song,,0,0,0,,Horses, cows, humans, watch closely!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:51.91,0:44:57.56,Song,,0,0,0,,See how frightening we are!
Dialogue: 10,0:44:51.91,0:44:53.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Just accept it already!
Dialogue: 10,0:44:57.56,0:44:58.37,Song,,0,0,0,,{sore}There!
Dialogue: 10,0:44:58.37,0:45:01.80,Song,,0,0,0,,No one will slip away!{"hitori mo nukasu na"}
Dialogue: 10,0:45:01.80,0:45:05.56,Song,,0,0,0,,And you're no exception! Inside you go!{"kimi made, saa te, saa! Naka he..."}
Dialogue: 0,0:45:10.47,0:45:14.73,Song,,0,0,0,,{"oretachi omae wo, --". From context: }We'll make sure the same fate befalls you!
Dialogue: 10,0:45:05.56,0:45:09.96,Default,,0,0,0,,The wind is strong today, \Nso the windmill's running at full power.
Dialogue: 10,0:45:16.49,0:45:19.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Right! I just have to stop the windmill.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:20.44,0:45:24.54,Song,,0,0,0,,Should we boil him? Or roast him?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:24.54,0:45:28.45,Song,,0,0,0,,The cook gets the final say!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:28.45,0:45:30.46,Song,,0,0,0,,Roast him and eat him with sauce?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:30.46,0:45:32.43,Song,,0,0,0,,Boil him and eat him with soy?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:32.43,0:45:34.63,Song,,0,0,0,,How should we cook him so he tastes the best?
Dialogue: 10,0:45:26.08,0:45:28.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{You klutz, what are you panicking for?}How clumsy! Why are you in such a hurry?
Dialogue: 10,0:45:30.71,0:45:33.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, I've seen you somewhere.
Dialogue: 10,0:45:36.21,0:45:38.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Where do you think you're going?
Dialogue: 10,0:45:38.80,0:45:41.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh... well... to the bathroom!
Dialogue: 10,0:45:42.32,0:45:44.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Useless brat!
Dialogue: 10,0:46:04.17,0:46:05.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Watch where you're going!
Dialogue: 10,0:46:05.93,0:46:07.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry...
Dialogue: 10,0:46:07.64,0:46:09.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! It's you!
Dialogue: 10,0:46:09.14,0:46:09.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Gotta run!
Dialogue: 10,0:46:09.79,0:46:10.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 10,0:46:34.46,0:46:35.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{yossho}Here we go!
Dialogue: 10,0:46:35.82,0:46:36.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Ow...
Dialogue: 10,0:46:38.78,0:46:39.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Ouch!
Dialogue: 10,0:47:22.49,0:47:24.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Everyone! Get over here!
Dialogue: 10,0:47:27.04,0:47:30.93,Song,,0,0,0,,Should we boil him? Or roast him?
Dialogue: 10,0:47:30.93,0:47:34.68,Song,,0,0,0,,{That's up to the cook's skills!}{???}The cook gets the final say!
Dialogue: 10,0:47:34.68,0:47:36.62,Song,,0,0,0,,Roast him and eat him with sauce?
Dialogue: 10,0:47:36.62,0:47:38.61,Song,,0,0,0,,Boil him and eat him with soy?
Dialogue: 10,0:47:38.61,0:47:40.59,Song,,0,0,0,,{What's the tastiest way to go about it?}{?????}How should we cook him so he tastes the best?
Dialogue: 10,0:47:51.83,0:47:54.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't wait to see what kind of demon he becomes.
Dialogue: 10,0:48:03.84,0:48:08.57,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on? \NThe wind is blowing, but the windmill has stopped.
Dialogue: 10,0:48:09.59,0:48:10.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't let go!
Dialogue: 10,0:48:11.58,0:48:20.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Heave-ho! Heave-ho! Heave-ho!\NHeave-ho! Heave-ho! Heave-ho! Heave-ho!
Dialogue: 10,0:48:20.52,0:48:22.34,Default,,0,0,0,,What's with this rickety thing?
Dialogue: 10,0:48:22.34,0:48:23.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{If you're so tough, come down here!}If you're looking for trouble, \Ncome down here!{"kuyashikattara", lib}
Dialogue: 10,0:48:24.32,0:48:26.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, everyone get Jack!
Dialogue: 10,0:48:32.91,0:48:35.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Think you're so tough?
Dialogue: 10,0:48:41.32,0:48:43.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Take this!
Dialogue: 10,0:48:43.40,0:48:44.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Ouch!
Dialogue: 10,0:49:03.84,0:49:04.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 10,0:49:59.08,0:50:00.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Run!
Dialogue: 10,0:50:05.15,0:50:06.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Kiki.
Dialogue: 10,0:50:06.85,0:50:08.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You failed.
Dialogue: 10,0:50:10.30,0:50:13.82,Default,,0,0,0,,As our laws dictate, \Nyou'll be sealed inside an iceberg.
Dialogue: 10,0:50:14.66,0:50:18.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll live in darkness, cold and alone.
Dialogue: 10,0:50:18.22,0:50:23.67,Default,,0,0,0,,In an icy mountain with no sound, \Nno light, frozen forever, Kiki!
Dialogue: 10,0:50:23.67,0:50:25.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Lady Grendel...
Dialogue: 10,0:50:25.60,0:50:26.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't forgive you!
Dialogue: 10,0:50:27.15,0:50:29.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{Not the bottom of the iceberg, please!}I'm begging you! Anything but that!
Dialogue: 10,0:50:30.03,0:50:32.59,Default,,0,0,0,,You think I'll forgive you?
Dialogue: 10,0:50:32.59,0:50:35.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Please! Please, Lady Grendel!
Dialogue: 10,0:50:37.60,0:50:39.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Cry if you want.
Dialogue: 10,0:50:39.98,0:50:42.16,Default,,0,0,0,,But will any tears come out?
Dialogue: 10,0:50:43.61,0:50:45.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Demons can't cry!
Dialogue: 10,0:50:45.84,0:50:48.48,Default,,0,0,0,,How cruel...
Dialogue: 10,0:50:48.48,0:50:50.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{That's so sad...}Don't you feel sorry for her?!
Dialogue: 10,0:50:50.49,0:50:52.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Ow!
Dialogue: 10,0:50:52.95,0:50:53.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Shibari!
Dialogue: 10,0:50:53.99,0:50:56.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{It's time for you to go, Kiki!}{????}It's time for your punishment, Kiki!
Dialogue: 10,0:50:57.75,0:50:59.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Go!
Dialogue: 10,0:51:19.64,0:51:23.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, let me go! I said free me! \NI'm gonna go home!
Dialogue: 10,0:51:23.96,0:51:26.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{I'll go home no matter what! Stop!}{???}Stop! I'm going back to the castle!
Dialogue: 10,0:51:26.29,0:51:27.85,Default,,0,0,0,,What's your problem?
Dialogue: 10,0:51:27.85,0:51:29.98,Default,,0,0,0,,You're Squeaky. Don't you understand?
Dialogue: 10,0:51:29.98,0:51:32.15,Default,,0,0,0,,What Squeaky? Who the hell is Squeaky?!
Dialogue: 10,0:51:32.15,0:51:34.15,Default,,0,0,0,,You used to be one of us!
Dialogue: 10,0:51:34.63,0:51:39.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a demon! Anyone who assaults\N a demon will pay dearly!
Dialogue: 10,0:51:56.56,0:51:58.01,Default,,0,0,0,,You cannot escape.
Dialogue: 10,0:51:58.01,0:52:00.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Come back, Jack!
Dialogue: 10,0:52:10.34,0:52:13.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Feels like we're going in circles.
Dialogue: 10,0:52:13.21,0:52:15.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Jack, something's not right.
Dialogue: 10,0:52:15.46,0:52:16.86,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just your imagination.
Dialogue: 10,0:52:16.86,0:52:19.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Look! There's the tunnel!
Dialogue: 10,0:52:26.46,0:52:28.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, this is bad!
Dialogue: 10,0:52:28.88,0:52:31.09,Default,,0,0,0,,We have to run!
Dialogue: 10,0:52:32.46,0:52:35.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone still thinks they can escape.
Dialogue: 10,0:52:41.81,0:52:44.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I went through hell, Lady Grendel!
Dialogue: 10,0:52:44.08,0:52:47.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{Those humans kidnapped a demon... outrageous!}That lot went and kidnapped a demon... Outrageous!
Dialogue: 10,0:52:50.85,0:52:51.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:52:54.99,0:52:56.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry!
Dialogue: 10,0:52:57.54,0:52:59.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm running as fast as I can!
Dialogue: 10,0:52:59.77,0:53:00.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 10,0:53:06.54,0:53:07.46,Default,,0,0,0,,This way!
Dialogue: 10,0:53:31.15,0:53:32.61,Default,,0,0,0,,The exit!
Dialogue: 10,0:53:43.29,0:53:47.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Everyone! Where did you go?!
Dialogue: 10,0:53:48.38,0:53:50.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, everyone!
Dialogue: 10,0:53:50.37,0:53:52.40,Default,,0,0,0,,No! Let go!
Dialogue: 10,0:53:52.40,0:53:53.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Let go!
Dialogue: 10,0:53:53.10,0:53:55.04,Default,,0,0,0,,What are these things?!
Dialogue: 10,0:54:08.42,0:54:09.81,Default,,0,0,0,,It's you, Jack!
Dialogue: 10,0:54:13.44,0:54:15.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine...
Dialogue: 10,0:54:16.57,0:54:18.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't lose!
Dialogue: 10,0:54:24.08,0:54:26.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{Why, you! You're a bad one!}Why, you! All of this is your fault!
Dialogue: 10,0:54:26.72,0:54:28.09,Default,,0,0,0,,What did I even do wrong?
Dialogue: 10,0:54:28.09,0:54:32.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Idiot, idiot, idiot! \NBecause of you, Kiki's going through hell!
Dialogue: 10,0:54:33.84,0:54:35.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Serves her right.
Dialogue: 10,0:54:35.28,0:54:37.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Sh-She's gonna get killed!
Dialogue: 10,0:54:38.81,0:54:39.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Killed?
Dialogue: 10,0:54:39.93,0:54:41.80,Default,,0,0,0,,It's your fault, demon!
Dialogue: 10,0:54:43.16,0:54:44.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's Kiki?!
Dialogue: 10,0:54:44.70,0:54:46.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Way down below.
Dialogue: 10,0:54:46.55,0:54:48.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Below? Hey, take me there.
Dialogue: 10,0:54:49.40,0:54:50.40,Default,,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 10,0:54:51.31,0:54:53.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you want to save her?
Dialogue: 10,0:54:53.32,0:54:57.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure I do, but going under the castle is scary!
Dialogue: 10,0:54:57.34,0:54:58.52,Default,,0,0,0,,What's it like down there?
Dialogue: 10,0:54:58.52,0:55:00.53,Default,,0,0,0,,A world of ice.
Dialogue: 10,0:55:00.53,0:55:01.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Ice?
Dialogue: 10,0:55:35.65,0:55:36.71,Default,,0,0,0,,It's cold.
Dialogue: 10,0:55:53.60,0:55:56.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Kiki! Kiki!
Dialogue: 10,0:55:59.32,0:56:00.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Kiki!
Dialogue: 10,0:56:01.48,0:56:02.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Kiki!
Dialogue: 10,0:56:12.02,0:56:13.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Kiki!
Dialogue: 10,0:56:13.58,0:56:15.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Kiki!
Dialogue: 10,0:56:22.59,0:56:23.80,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no need to panic.
Dialogue: 10,0:56:23.80,0:56:27.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{Even if Jack says comes, \Nyour fate stays the same.}Underneath the castle, \NJack will simply share her fate.{lit. "where Jack went, the same fate will befall him"}
Dialogue: 10,0:56:38.96,0:56:40.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Kiki!
Dialogue: 10,0:56:42.92,0:56:44.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Kiki!
Dialogue: 10,0:56:52.43,0:56:53.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Kiki!
Dialogue: 10,0:56:57.11,0:56:59.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Kiki! Kiki!
Dialogue: 10,0:57:01.36,0:57:03.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Kiki! Kiki!
Dialogue: 10,0:57:10.26,0:57:11.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Kiki!
Dialogue: 10,0:57:30.20,0:57:31.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Look closely.
Dialogue: 10,0:57:31.88,0:57:37.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Jack will soon freeze too. \NThis is what happens to anyone who opposes me.
Dialogue: 10,0:58:08.66,0:58:09.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm freezing!
Dialogue: 10,0:58:18.00,0:58:21.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Kiki! Hang in there!
Dialogue: 10,0:58:22.58,0:58:26.19,Default,,0,0,0,,However hard this may be, don't die on me!
Dialogue: 10,0:59:25.42,0:59:27.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm safe!
Dialogue: 10,0:59:27.67,0:59:29.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Safe!
Dialogue: 10,0:59:30.66,0:59:32.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm safe!
Dialogue: 10,0:59:32.55,0:59:35.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Jack saved me!
Dialogue: 10,0:59:48.27,0:59:51.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Right! Jack! Where's Jack?
Dialogue: 10,1:00:04.16,1:00:05.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Jack!
Dialogue: 10,1:00:16.99,1:00:19.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Jack! Jack!
Dialogue: 10,1:00:19.24,1:00:22.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Jack! Jack, Jack! Jack!
Dialogue: 10,1:00:27.35,1:00:30.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Jack! Jack! Jack!
Dialogue: 10,1:00:36.19,1:00:37.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Jack is dead.
Dialogue: 10,1:00:39.16,1:00:41.25,Default,,0,0,0,,He died trying to save me.
Dialogue: 10,1:00:58.26,1:01:00.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Jack...
Dialogue: 10,1:01:04.70,1:01:05.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Jack...
Dialogue: 10,1:01:17.61,1:01:19.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Jack! Jack!
Dialogue: 10,1:01:24.49,1:01:25.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Kiki!
Dialogue: 10,1:01:25.79,1:01:26.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Jack!
Dialogue: 10,1:01:26.98,1:01:28.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Kiki!
Dialogue: 10,1:01:28.35,1:01:29.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Jack.
Dialogue: 10,1:01:29.42,1:01:30.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Kiki.
Dialogue: 10,1:02:43.74,1:02:45.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Have a taste of my pain and sorrow!
Dialogue: 10,1:03:00.05,1:03:04.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Give up, Kiki. Your magic is gone.
Dialogue: 10,1:03:04.17,1:03:09.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{Ever since you shed tears, you lost your power.}The moment you shed tears, you lost your power.
Dialogue: 10,1:03:12.48,1:03:15.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Die! Perish, you fools!
Dialogue: 10,1:04:51.61,1:04:53.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Jack!
Dialogue: 10,1:04:53.54,1:04:55.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm losing patience.
Dialogue: 10,1:04:55.18,1:04:58.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Why won't he put more effort into it?
Dialogue: 10,1:05:21.57,1:05:26.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Hey, you lot! \NGimme some food!{やいやい again}
Dialogue: 10,1:05:26.23,1:05:27.86,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't have anything!
Dialogue: 10,1:05:27.86,1:05:29.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be stingy!
Dialogue: 10,1:05:29.76,1:05:31.58,Default,,0,0,0,,This is no time for that!
Dialogue: 10,1:05:36.02,1:05:38.41,Default,,0,0,0,,That's it! You did it!
Dialogue: 10,1:05:38.41,1:05:40.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, this is bad!
Dialogue: 10,1:06:15.99,1:06:16.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Jack!
Dialogue: 10,1:06:16.81,1:06:21.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! If you won't hand over food, fine.
Dialogue: 10,1:06:21.03,1:06:23.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll bite your nose off instead!
Dialogue: 10,1:06:23.71,1:06:24.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 10,1:06:24.61,1:06:26.13,Default,,0,0,0,,You said it!
Dialogue: 10,1:06:26.13,1:06:28.96,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this stupid crystal ball?!
Dialogue: 10,1:06:29.43,1:06:30.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't see! Can't see!
Dialogue: 10,1:06:30.97,1:06:32.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 10,1:06:32.23,1:06:33.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not moving an inch! {lit: won't show you [what's in the ball]}
Dialogue: 10,1:06:33.91,1:06:35.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop messing with us!
Dialogue: 10,1:06:35.16,1:06:36.68,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 10,1:06:40.82,1:06:44.63,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, then! If you want to see it so badly...
Dialogue: 10,1:06:45.53,1:06:47.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll do this!
Dialogue: 10,1:07:36.39,1:07:41.18,Default,,0,0,0,,How's that? You want to look? \NYou want to, right?!
Dialogue: 10,1:07:41.18,1:07:43.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry and take off that cloak!
Dialogue: 10,1:07:43.73,1:07:45.44,Default,,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 10,1:07:45.44,1:07:47.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You meanie!
Dialogue: 10,1:07:47.58,1:07:51.30,Default,,0,0,0,,If you want to see it, \Ngimme something to eat! Go on!
Dialogue: 10,1:07:53.43,1:07:55.84,Default,,0,0,0,,C'mon, you want to take a look, right?
Dialogue: 10,1:08:19.78,1:08:23.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm hungry. So hungry!
Dialogue: 10,1:08:26.97,1:08:32.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm hungry. I'm hungry. I'm hungry!
Dialogue: 10,1:08:37.10,1:08:38.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Jack, hang in there!
Dialogue: 10,1:08:38.36,1:08:40.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Go, Jack! Go!
Dialogue: 10,1:08:42.02,1:08:43.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 10,1:08:43.10,1:08:46.64,Default,,0,0,0,,You think I'm gonna let you have all the fun?!
Dialogue: 10,1:08:47.86,1:08:49.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine...
Dialogue: 10,1:08:51.65,1:08:55.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Cut it out! Cut it out, I said!
Dialogue: 10,1:09:24.43,1:09:26.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, how about this?!
Dialogue: 10,1:09:34.74,1:09:37.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! The magic is dispelled!
Dialogue: 10,1:09:38.83,1:09:42.22,Default,,0,0,0,,So this crystal ball was the source of magic.
Dialogue: 10,1:09:42.22,1:09:44.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, then we'll smash it!
Dialogue: 10,1:09:44.50,1:09:47.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay! Leave it to me.
Dialogue: 10,1:10:04.98,1:10:06.81,Default,,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 10,1:10:12.14,1:10:13.23,Default,,0,0,0,,You witch!{Yarou! - more literal would be Bastard! or Bitch!, but this is a kids' movie}
Dialogue: 10,1:10:18.45,1:10:20.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You damn demon!
Dialogue: 10,1:10:33.17,1:10:35.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Watch out, Jack!
Dialogue: 10,1:10:53.65,1:10:55.12,Default,,0,0,0,,What was that?!
Dialogue: 10,1:10:59.16,1:11:00.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Kiki!
Dialogue: 10,1:11:01.28,1:11:02.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Shibari!
Dialogue: 10,1:11:02.26,1:11:03.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Kiki!
Dialogue: 10,1:11:04.04,1:11:06.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Shibari, which way did the witch go?
Dialogue: 10,1:11:06.65,1:11:07.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know!
Dialogue: 10,1:11:07.86,1:11:10.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, that weird creature? It went that way.
Dialogue: 10,1:11:11.71,1:11:13.85,Default,,0,0,0,,That's her! Okay...
Dialogue: 10,1:11:44.15,1:11:45.62,Default,,0,0,0,,There she is!
Dialogue: 10,1:11:52.38,1:11:55.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{Chasing me without knowing anything...}He's chasing me, not knowing any better.
Dialogue: 10,1:12:25.93,1:12:27.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 10,1:12:28.24,1:12:29.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Get off me!
Dialogue: 10,1:12:36.04,1:12:37.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't get in our way!
Dialogue: 10,1:12:42.26,1:12:44.00,Default,,0,0,0,,She's trying to escape!
Dialogue: 10,1:12:58.50,1:13:08.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll come back someday and take revenge\N on all of you! A witch's curse lasts forever!
Dialogue: 10,1:13:20.80,1:13:22.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Are we too late?
Dialogue: 10,1:13:28.68,1:13:30.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{Somebody! Somebody catch onto me!}{hippatte = to pull - not sure what he means}Someone! Someone, help me pull it down!
Dialogue: 10,1:13:32.76,1:13:34.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{Catch onto me!}Grab hold of the rope!
Dialogue: 10,1:13:47.62,1:13:49.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Off she goes. I'd hoped that box would hold her down.{"ano hako mo to burasagete icchatta"}
Dialogue: 10,1:13:50.66,1:13:53.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatever, we can't stop her now.
Dialogue: 10,1:13:53.18,1:13:55.49,Default,,0,0,0,,More importantly, let's save everyone else.
Dialogue: 10,1:14:04.26,1:14:11.74,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll all be blown away with the castle \Nwhen that time bomb goes off!
Dialogue: 10,1:15:11.70,1:15:13.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Over there.
Dialogue: 10,1:15:23.04,1:15:26.21,Default,,0,0,0,,She's flying so erratically. Think she'd drunk?
Dialogue: 10,1:15:51.36,1:15:52.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 10,1:16:04.25,1:16:05.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Run away!
Dialogue: 10,1:16:25.54,1:16:27.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Run! Run!
Dialogue: 10,1:16:43.39,1:16:44.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You can do it!
Dialogue: 10,1:16:51.90,1:16:53.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Get back here!
Dialogue: 10,1:16:54.26,1:16:56.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{Careful!}{???}Hold up, dammit!{"matanai ka, kono"}
Dialogue: 10,1:16:58.47,1:16:59.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 10,1:16:59.99,1:17:01.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, help!
Dialogue: 10,1:16:59.99,1:17:02.53,Overlap,,0,0,0,,Squeaky! Get back!
Dialogue: 10,1:17:01.66,1:17:05.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop! You big meanie!
Dialogue: 10,1:17:21.04,1:17:22.61,Default,,0,0,0,,The magic is gone!
Dialogue: 10,1:17:22.61,1:17:25.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Kiki, you turned back into a human.
Dialogue: 10,1:17:29.62,1:17:30.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so glad!
Dialogue: 0,1:17:30.17,1:17:45.60,Song,,0,0,0,,{On this bright new day, as the sun shines on us}{honestly no clue}On this bright new day, the sun smiles down on us{"-- ni, ohi-sama ga hohoemu". From context.}
Dialogue: 0,1:17:45.60,1:17:53.27,Song,,0,0,0,,Good morning, good morning
Dialogue: 0,1:17:53.27,1:18:00.80,Song,,0,0,0,,May you have fun forever and ever
Dialogue: 0,1:18:00.80,1:18:15.96,Song,,0,0,0,,{Sing the festival song, sing of a happy morning}Even the birds are singing this cheerful morning song{"kotori mo uta oru, tanoshii asa no uta wo"}
Dialogue: 0,1:18:15.96,1:18:23.56,Song,,0,0,0,,Good morning, good morning
Dialogue: 0,1:18:23.57,1:18:45.87,Song,,0,0,0,,We wish you happiness, forever and ever and ever
